Interface Spectrum

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DtaSpectrum, Ms2Query, Ms2Spectrum, MzDataSpectrum, MzXMLSpectrum, PklSpectrum, SpectrumImplementation

    public interface Spectrum
    Represents a spectrum in the parsed peak list file.
    Author:
    jg
